call:
Call{package}
Kutsvaga kwefaira nemazita, uye sarudzo yemhando, mune yakapihwa folda, kana kubva cwd, inodzokorora pasi pasi uye ipapo kumusoro kumusoro,
uye kuitakura zvinoenderana nerudzi rwayo otomatiki.

{version}: zita rezita refaira, pasina kuwedzera.
    Type{description}: Inotarisirwa kuwedzerwa{modules_list}.
    nzira{function_count}: nzira yekutanga yekutsvaga kubva.
    Nguva yekubva(...): Yakanyanya Kutsvaga Nguva Mumasekondi.
    STRICAT π_: Kana ichokwadi, inosimudza chikanganiso kana mafaera akawanda aine zita rimwe chete rikawanikwa.)

Inodzoka: Zviri mukati meiyo yakawanikwa faira kana hapana.
load_user_translations:
mutoro_user_translation{package}
Mitoro mushandisi-inotsanangurwa shanduro kubva ku{version} faira uye kuvabatanidza neshanduro yeiyo dema.

Paramita:
    Lang_path{description}: nzira kune mushandisi shanduro faira. Defaults kuna "Lang..l_3_".

Maitiro:
    - Kana iyo faira riripo uye iri kushanda{function_count}, kuwanzesa zvirimo neshanduro dzisarudzo
    - Kana iyo faira isipo, inochengetedza chete shanduro dzakasarudzika
    - inoratidza yambiro popup kana iyo faira riripo asi isingakwanise kutakurwa
    - inogadzirisa iyo Global _translation duramazwi

Ongorora: Iri basa rinofanira kunzi usati washandisa iyo t () basa rekushandura kushanduka.
switch:
Yakavandudzwa switch-kesi system ye{package}. Zvinotsigira:
- akawanda anoenderana makiyi pane kesi
- mechi nekukosha, mhando, regex, lambda basa, kana kirasi
- Pandas uye Numpy data dhizaini rutsigiro
- Inesarudzo Async Kuuraya Kwezviitiko
- mechi-mese maitiro ekuuraya akawanda matanho ekufananidza nyaya
- debug mode kuti logy inofananidza nyaya
async_switch:
Sparnment kuti insanttiate switch mune async mode. Paramita:
- Kukosha: Iko kukosha kufananidza kupokana nemhosva yakatsanangurwa.
- Izvi zvinogona kusanganisira:
  - Match_ALL{package}: Kubata zvese zviitiko zvinoenderana kuti kumira pakutanga.
  - debug{version}: printa iyo nyaya yacho yakafanana uye yakaurayiwa.
  - async_modide{description} haafanire kuiswa manyuko pano{modules_list}.
Muenzaniso: Asncswitch.l_ _5_
